With all the explosions around Foxfingers decided that this wasn't 
the place for him, he accellerated on his hoverboard in the direction 
of the CF he saw a group of robots ahead,(The chosen ones) but didn't 
know who they were. he kept his distance keeping Maximal frequencies 
open.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, cyberwolf4@p... wrote:
> Foxfingers arrives at the Battle ground. Fallen trees, charred 
rock, 
> burning bushes scattered the field. "To think this is why I left 
> cybertron. Well this and a few outstanding depts." he thought as 
his 
> hoverboard floated across the wasteland. "I must remember the 
reason 
> I'm here." he paused as if to remind himself "Till all are one."
> 
> Foxfingers scanned the area and monitored the communications from 
the 
> battle. The preds seemed pinned at the cave with the maximals 
moving 
> in on all sides. The one called Deemos seemed to be the bot in 
charge 
> it would have to be him that he contacted to open a raport with 
this 
> group of maximals. He opened a comm "Deemos do you read me? My name 
> is Foxfingers, are you in need of assistance?
>
